  (24, 19, 'garage', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your garage appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The garage is in overall good condition but requires some attention to several identified issues to maintain its functionality and safety. These include structural concerns and operational inefficiencies.', '["Several large cracks in the garage floor.","Loud noise during garage door operation.","Noticeable water stains present in the garage.","Lack of ventilation causing dampness.","Outdated fixtures with faulty wiring noted."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor and fill the cracks in the garage floor to prevent further deterioration.","Consider servicing the garage door to reduce noise and ensure proper operation.","Identify the source of water stains and resolve any leaks or drainage issues.","Enhance ventilation to reduce dampness and improve air quality in the garage.","Upgrade outdated fixtures and ensure all wiring is inspected and repaired by a professional."]'::jsonb, 'General Contractor', 'Within the next 3-6 months', 26, '2025-12-16T23:36:36.175Z', '2025-12-16T23:36:42.818Z'),
