  (33, 20, 'garage', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your garage appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The garage is in good condition, but there are a few areas that could benefit from some attention. This seems more about routine maintenance than major concerns.', '["Several large cracks might suggest settling or minor structural shifts","common in garages over time.","Loud noise during operation could indicate the need for lubrication or maintenance of the garage door mechanism.","Noticeable water stains could imply previous leaks or moisture issues","particularly if there''s a lack of ventilation.","No ventilation might contribute to dampness","potentially leading to mold or mildew problems.","Exposed wires and electrical risks require attention to ensure safety."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the cracks to see if they expand or change significantly.","Keep an eye on the noise level","as sustained loud noises may suggest a developing issue with garage door components.","Watch for any new water stain patterns after rainfall to determine if leaks are active.","Consider solutions to improve ventilation to manage humidity.","Address electrical risks as soon as possible to ensure a safe environment."]'::jsonb, NULL, '1-3 months', 26, '2025-12-19T21:14:12.575Z', '2025-12-19T21:14:17.838Z'),
