  (50, 85066, 'hvac', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Fair', 'Fair', '["Some minor issues detected in your hvac","Consider scheduling a professional inspection soon","Regular maintenance recommended"]'::jsonb, 'Your HVAC system seems to be performing adequately, with minor issues that may affect long-term efficiency. Routine maintenance is keeping things operational but not optimal.', '["The HVAC system has been serviced within the last year","which is beneficial.","There is no unusual noise reported","indicating no immediate mechanical failures.","The system is currently clean and free of debris","reducing the risk of airflow issues."]'::jsonb, '["Continue with regular maintenance to ensure efficiency.","Monitor for any changes in performance or unusual noises.","Consider a professional check-up before the next extreme weather season."]'::jsonb, 'HVAC', 'Annual routine maintenance is recommended within the next 6 months.', 8, '2025-12-25T17:15:39.295Z', '2025-12-25T17:15:41.597Z'),
  (51, 85066, 'roof', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your roof appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your roof appears to be in good condition overall, with no major issues reported. However, there are a couple of areas to keep an eye on to ensure long-term performance.', '["Cracked or curled shingles are present.","No visible issues with flashing were noted.","Gutters appear to be separated or sagging.","Shingles have a consistent color and uniform lines."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the cracked or curled shingles to see if they worsen","which could lead to leaks.","Regularly check the state of gutters to avoid water overflow and potential damage to the exterior walls.","Ensure that no further separation or sagging happens with the gutters to prevent water pooling."]'::jsonb, 'Roofing', 'Consider having a roofing professional assess and potentially repair within the next 6-12 months to prevent escalation.', 8, '2025-12-25T17:18:16.791Z', '2025-12-25T17:18:19.982Z'),
  (52, 21, 'kitchen', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your kitchen appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The kitchen appears to be in generally good condition with a few minor concerns to monitor. There is some built-up grease and water pooling that should be addressed to ensure the cleanliness and safety of the area.', '["Dry and dusty surfaces","Clean tiles","Smooth and shiny finishes","Water pooling in certain areas","Built-up grease on some surfaces"]'::jsonb, '["Regularly clean and check for water pooling to prevent slipping hazards.","Address built-up grease with appropriate cleaners to maintain cleanliness.","Ensure all surfaces are dry to prevent long-term water damage."]'::jsonb, 'General Cleaning', 'Watch for changes over the next few weeks and clean regularly.', 25, '2025-12-27T22:32:10.570Z', '2025-12-27T22:32:13.001Z'),
  (53, 85061, 'cabinetry', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Fair', 'Fair', '["Some minor issues detected in your cabinetry","Consider scheduling a professional inspection soon","Regular maintenance recommended"]'::jsonb, 'The kitchen cabinetry shows signs of moderate wear and may require some attention. This includes minor surface damage, potential signs of mold, and an odd smell which might indicate a deeper issue with materials or maintenance.', '["Visible surface damage such as scratches or dents detected.","Signs of possible mold or mildew growth noted.","Presence of an unusual chemical smell.","Sticky residue upon touching","indicating possible finish degradation."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor for any progression in damage or mold growth","especially after high humidity conditions.","Consider cleaning the surfaces with a mild detergent to remove residues and smell.","If the odor persists","investigate further for any hidden mold or issues."]'::jsonb, 'Carpentry', 'Within the next month', 26, '2025-12-30T03:10:46.108Z', '2025-12-30T03:10:49.256Z'),
  (54, 85061, 'project_rescue', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your project_rescue appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your foundation project has been stalled, and while the overall condition seems manageable, it''s important to address the unfinished state. The current environment indicates regular maintenance but also shows signs of stalled progress, particularly with visible diagonal cracks and contractor communication issues.', '["The project involves the foundation","a critical structure for the house.","Diagonal cracks have been noted","which may indicate some underlying structural concerns.","The contractor has stalled communication","with no written agreement present."]'::jsonb, '["Document all current work and any missing tasks or items.","Consider consulting multiple contractors to obtain quotes for finishing the project.","Maintain regular lawn and landscaping to prevent further issues around the foundation.","Monitor the diagonal cracks for any changes in size or propagation."]'::jsonb, 'Foundation specialist', 'Consider getting professional assessments within the next few weeks to plan necessary work.', 26, '2025-12-30T03:12:00.969Z', '2025-12-30T03:12:04.124Z'),
  (55, 85061, 'project_rescue', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your project_rescue appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The bedroom project is cosmetically incomplete with some quality issues in the existing work, such as fading or sagging surfaces. There are signs of moisture-related problems, including damp or discolored areas and condensation.', '["Cosmetically incomplete project in the bedroom.","Quality issues include fading or sagging and poor workmanship.","Condensation or moisture leading to damp areas."]'::jsonb, '["Ensure proper ventilation to reduce condensation and dampness.","Keep a list of all incomplete cosmetic aspects for future reference.","Consider documenting moisture areas for any necessary corrections."]'::jsonb, 'General Contractor', 'Within the next 2-3 months', 26, '2025-12-31T18:29:18.183Z', '2025-12-31T18:29:22.521Z'),
  (56, 85061, 'bathroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bathroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Quick take for your bathroom: Good.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 26, '2025-12-31T22:28:56.450Z', '2025-12-31T22:29:35.732Z'),
  (57, 85061, 'bathroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Fair', 'Fair', '["Some minor issues detected in your bathroom","Consider scheduling a professional inspection soon","Regular maintenance recommended"]'::jsonb, 'Your bathroom is in fair condition, showing normal wear and tear. The areas to focus on are the slightly slow drain and general maintenance tasks typical for this stage.', '["The bathroom appears dry","indicating no immediate moisture issues.","The drain is a bit slow","which suggests some minor blockage or buildup.","The fixtures look solid and well-sealed","which is positive."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the drain speed. If it slows further","consider using a drain cleaner or scheduling a clean-out.","Check seals periodically to ensure they remain intact and no leaks develop.","Maintain ventilation to prevent future moisture-related problems."]'::jsonb, 'Plumbing', '1-3 months', 26, '2026-01-01T22:03:42.247Z', '2026-01-01T22:03:44.727Z'),
  (58, 85061, 'bathroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Fair', 'Fair', '["Some minor issues detected in your bathroom","Consider scheduling a professional inspection soon","Regular maintenance recommended"]'::jsonb, 'The bathroom is currently experiencing some moderate wear and tear issues that should be monitored and addressed in due course to avoid escalation. The presence of water stains and soft spots could suggest potential water damage, requiring attention to prevent further deterioration.', '["Water stains and soft spots could indicate a water leak","possibly around fixtures or from pipes.","A very slow or backed-up drain can be a sign of clogging or issues with plumbing","which can worsen over time.","Small cracks or gaps","while often cosmetic","can lead to water intrusion and further damage if not sealed."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor soft spots to ensure they don''t expand","indicating worsening water damage.","Address the slow drain promptly to prevent complete blockage.","Seal cracks to prevent water penetration and maintain structural integrity."]'::jsonb, 'Plumbing', 'Within the next month', 26, '2026-01-02T14:05:11.162Z', '2026-01-02T14:05:19.605Z'),
  (59, 21, 'bedroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bedroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The bedroom is largely in good condition with minor issues identified that are common and typically expected over time. Though there''s a bit of stuffiness and some small hairline cracks, these issues do not require immediate attention and are generally non-structural.', '["No significant issues noticed.","Room feels a bit stuffy or dry.","Small hairline cracks present."]'::jsonb, '["Consider using a dehumidifier or air purifier to improve air quality and manage dryness.","Monitor the hairline cracks to ensure they do not widen or deepen","which could indicate a larger issue."]'::jsonb, NULL, NULL, 25, '2026-01-03T03:03:35.901Z', '2026-01-03T03:04:09.783Z'),
