  (63, 85073, 'kitchen', 'full', '{}'::jsonb, 'Fair', 'Fair', '["Some minor issues detected in your kitchen","Consider scheduling a professional inspection soon","Regular maintenance recommended"]'::jsonb, 'The kitchen issues suggest moderate functionality with signs of water damage and drainage problems. This is likely not immediately urgent but should be monitored and addressed incrementally to prevent further damage.', '["Water stains and swelling","indicating possible long-term water exposure.","Backups and gurgles","suggesting drainage issues.","Leaks during or after dishwasher operation.","Intermittent leaks or puddles","possibly linked to plumbing connections.","Soft or loose spots suggesting underlying structural concerns.","Dishwasher does not clear effectively","indicating maintenance or clogging issues."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor for worsening water stains or swelling","which can indicate ongoing leaks or moisture issues.","Check for any soft spots becoming larger","as this may indicate water intrusion affecting the subfloor.","Keep an eye on the frequency and severity of backups; increasing frequency may require intervention.","Inspect dishwasher seals and connections if leaks persist to prevent further water damage."]'::jsonb, 'Plumbing', 'Review and plan to address over the next few months.', 26, '2026-01-11T19:07:50.856Z', '2026-01-11T19:07:55.669Z'),
  (64, 85073, 'bathroom', 'full', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bathroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your bathroom is in generally good condition with a few areas needing minor attention. The issues noted are common in many bathrooms and do not indicate severe structural problems at this point.', '["Water stains and soft spots are present","possibly indicating minor water intrusion or insufficient ventilation.","The drain backs up slowly and clogs are frequent","suggesting a need for regular maintenance or minor plumbing adjustment.","Tiles are loose or caulking is missing","which could lead to water seepage if not addressed."]'::jsonb, '["Check and clear the drains regularly to prevent further clogs.","Re-caulk or re-secure loose tiles to prevent water damage.","Consider improving ventilation to reduce steam and dampness","which can prevent mold growth."]'::jsonb, 'Plumbing', 'Address within the next 1-2 months to prevent minor issues from escalating.', 26, '2026-01-11T19:11:12.937Z', '2026-01-11T19:11:16.435Z'),
  (65, 85073, 'bathroom', 'full', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bathroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your bathroom is generally in good condition, but there are some issues that need attention to prevent them from becoming more significant in the future.', '["Water stains and soft spots may suggest minor water leakage.","The drain backing up and frequent clogs indicate a plumbing issue.","Tiles becoming loose or missing caulk can lead to water damage.","The bathroom remains steamy","suggesting inadequate ventilation."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor for worsening of water stains or any change in wall or ceiling texture.","Try using a drain cleaner or a plumbing snake to address slow drainage.","Re-apply or replace missing caulk to prevent moisture intrusion.","Enhance bathroom ventilation by using the exhaust fan effectively","or consider upgrading it if necessary."]'::jsonb, 'Plumbing', 'Next few months', 26, '2026-01-11T19:14:07.697Z', '2026-01-11T19:14:14.241Z'),
  (66, 85073, 'bedroom', 'full', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bedroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The bedroom seems to be generally in good condition, but there are a few concerns regarding maintenance and functionality that should be observed. These include growing stains, temperature control issues, and difficulty with windows.', '["Growing stain noted in the room.","Difficulty in regulating temperature (often too hot/cold).","Windows are hard to open or close."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the stain for any increase in size or changes in color to determine if it''s a sign of a leak or other issue.","Consider checking the HVAC system or insulation for efficiency issues affecting temperature control.","Inspect the windows to ensure they aren''t misaligned or swollen due to humidity."]'::jsonb, 'General Maintenance', 'Assess and monitor over the next 2-4 weeks.', 26, '2026-01-11T19:15:43.486Z', '2026-01-11T19:15:47.775Z'),
  (67, 85073, 'bedroom', 'full', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bedroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your current concerns in the bedroom relate to minor structural issues and aesthetics, primarily revolving around stains on the walls, fluctuating temperature, and window functionality. These issues, while observable, don''t immediately suggest severe problems but do deserve attention to maintain comfort and prevent potential escalation.', '["Growing stains on the walls.","Temperature often too hot or too cold","indicating possible HVAC inefficiency.","Windows are hard to open and close","possibly due to misalignment or age."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the stains for further growth or dampness","which could indicate water intrusion.","Check seals around windows and inspect if the thermostat or vents are functioning properly.","Consider inspecting window frames if difficulty in operation persists to avoid worsening."]'::jsonb, 'HVAC', '1-2 months', 26, '2026-01-11T19:17:44.126Z', '2026-01-11T19:17:48.339Z'),
