  (85, 85077, 'kitchen', 'full', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your kitchen appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your kitchen is currently under construction with visible progress being made. While some normal wear and minor swelling are observed, most systems appear to function properly where completed. The absence of a hood/fan is noted, and utility hook-ups are pending.', '["Exposed walls and unfinished surfaces are part of current construction.","Appliances are on-site but not yet installed.","Drain systems are working well","but water supply lines still need to be connected.","Minor signs of swelling","likely from recent construction activities."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor any swelling areas for changes that could indicate a need for adjustments.","Plan for the installation of a kitchen hood/fan for adequate ventilation once construction allows.","Keep an eye on water connections once installed for any leaks or issues.","Ensure appliance installation includes correct leveling and hook-ups when ready."]'::jsonb, NULL, 'Monitor during the next 4-8 weeks as construction progresses.', 26, '2026-01-11T21:25:58.451Z', '2026-01-11T21:39:42.389Z'),
