  (96, 85089, 'bathroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bathroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The bathroom seems to be functioning well, with good drainage and no signs of excessive moisture. While there are small cracks or gaps, they appear manageable and typical for wear over time.', '["Bathroom drains quickly","indicating no clogging.","No signs of moisture-related issues with surfaces remaining dry.","Small cracks or gaps in the bathroom surfaces."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the small cracks or gaps to ensure they don''t widen.","If cracks increase","consider applying a sealant for cosmetic maintenance."]'::jsonb, NULL, 'Monitor over the next 3 to 6 months for any changes.', 96, '2026-01-21T17:22:28.247Z', '2026-01-21T17:23:32.383Z'),
  (97, 32, 'bathroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bathroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your bathroom is in good condition overall. It''s common for caulk to degrade or for tiles to loosen over time due to regular use and moisture exposure.', '["The tiles appear to be loose or there is missing caulk.","The drains are functioning well and the area is dry."]'::jsonb, '["Keep an eye on the loose tile as it could lead to water seeping underneath","potentially causing water damage over time.","Plan to reapply caulk to areas where it''s missing to prevent moisture from penetrating the gaps."]'::jsonb, NULL, 'Next 1-3 months', 63, '2026-01-24T20:52:53.454Z', '2026-01-24T20:54:53.863Z'),
  (98, 85083, 'bedroom', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your bedroom appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'The bedroom appears well-maintained overall. The stain on the wall could be indicative of an underlying issue, while the room feels slightly stuffy or dry despite looking normal otherwise.', '["Stain seems to be growing","which suggests potential for underlying moisture or leakage issues.","Room feels a bit stuffy or dry","common in many homes especially during certain seasons."]'::jsonb, '["Monitor the stain for changes in size","shape","or color","as these could indicate a hidden leak or moisture problem.","Consider using a humidifier to improve air quality","especially if the room consistently feels dry."]'::jsonb, NULL, 'Monitor over the next few weeks.', 87, '2026-01-24T21:41:20.078Z', '2026-01-24T21:41:57.902Z'),
