  (100, 85090, 'kitchen', 'lite', '{}'::jsonb, 'Good', 'Good', '["Your kitchen appears to be in good working condition","No major concerns identified during this check"]'::jsonb, 'Your kitchen''s current condition seems generally positive with some areas needing attention, particularly regarding the electrical outlet protections and drainage system.', '["The kitchen area overall appears dry and in good condition.","The drainage is efficient in some parts","but some areas drain slowly or leave water.","An electrical outlet (GFCI) seems to trip frequently and won''t reset."]'::jsonb, '["For the slow drain","consider cleaning the trap to see if it improves drainage speed.","Investigate the tripping electrical outlet to ensure it''s functioning correctly and not overloaded."]'::jsonb, 'Plumbing', 'Inspect tripping GFCI: ASAP; Drain cleaning: Soon', 26, '2026-02-03T17:43:23.370Z', '2026-02-03T17:43:33.480Z'),
